иля повествователем низкого социального",536878826]],["^15",[2963,"^O","^1;",536878775]],["^15",[2963,"^F",2957,536878775]],["^15",[2963,"^X",73,536878775]],["^15",[2963,"^V",2555,536878775]],["^15",[2963,"^U",73,536878776]],["^15",[2963,"^;","~u688a5098-b9a5-4c39-be6d-8dbc2c5e7b1a",536878775]],["^15",[2965,"^Q","Изобилие художественных приемов",536878867]],["^15",[2965,"^O","^1;",536878842]],["^15",[2965,"^F",2963,536878842]],["^15",[2965,"^X",73,536878842]],["^15",[2965,"^V",2555,536878842]],["^15",[2965,"^U",73,536878843]],["^15",[2965,"^;","~u688a51f1-b1b0-4642-9f6a-607db31179c1",536878842]],["^15",[2966,"^Q","Женщина высокого социального стиля, но не в словах",536878955]],["^15",[2966,"^O","^1;",536878888]],["^15",[2966,"^F",2958,536878888]],["^15",[2966,"^X",73,536878888]],["^15",[2966,"^V",2671,536878888]],["^15",[2966,"^U",73,536878889]],["^15",[2966,"^;","~u688a5445-ad93-46e0-b399-113ce73c6269",536878888]],["^15",[2967,"^12",2,536878959]],["^15",[2972,"^Q","speech errors are just one manifestation of a broad phenomenon that concerns categories in general, and which reveals itself in various contexts, including physical actions. Action errors, too, have their own eloquent fashion of showing how conceptual wires can get crossed thanks to analogies\nls-type:: annotation\nhl-page:: 513\nhl-color:: yellow\nid:: 688b9cea-744c-4cfd-b9e8-bfd4b7aa08f9",536878991]],["^15",[2972,"^O","^1;",536878991]],["^15",[2972,"^@",false,536878991]],["^15",[2972,"^F",2934,536878991]],["^15",[2972,"^X",2302,536878991]],["^15",[2972,"^V",2302,536878991]],["^15",[2972,"^U",2302,536878992]],["^15",[2972,"^?",["^ ","^1Y","annotation","^1Z",513,"^1[","yellow","^1D","688b9cea-744c-4cfd-b9e8-bfd4b7aa08f9"],536878991]],["^15",[2972,"^J",["^14",["^1Y","^1Z","^1[","^1D"]],536878991]],["^15",[2972,"^4",["^ ","^1Y","annotation","^1Z","513","^1[","yellow","^1D","688b9cea-744c-4cfd-b9e8-bfd4b7aa08f9"],536878991]],["^15",[2972,"^;","~u688b9cea-744c-4cfd-b9e8-bfd4b7aa08f9",536878991]],["^15",[2973,"^Q","((68924991-383c-4727-9945-525d41207af2))((689249b0-4392-4470-ad65-6a890661b47a))",536879737]],["^15",[2973,"^O","^1;",536879008]],["^15",[2973,"^F",3025,536879767]],["^15",[2973,"^X",1000,536879008]],["^15",[2973,"^V",3025,536879767]],["^15",[2973,"^U",1000,536879802]],["^15",[2973,"^U",3020,536879802]],["^15",[2973,"^U",3021,536879802]],["^15",[2973,"^?",["^ "],536879737]],["^15",[2973,"^H",3020,536879737]],["^15",[2973,"^H",3021,536879737]],["^15",[2973,"^;","~u688b9d06-4b2f-47b3-97c3-297019e95c62",536879008]],["^15",[2974,"^12",2,536879015]],["^15",[2977,"^12",2,536879046]],["^15",[2979,"^K",1754249596249,536879060]],["^15",[2979,"^@",false,536879060]],["^15",[2979,"^Y","middle-earth/languages",536879060]],["^15",[2979,"^A",2980,536879060]],["^15",[2979,"^11","Middle-earth/languages",536879060]],["^15",[2979,"^B",1754249596249,536879060]],["^15",[2979,"^;","~u688fb97c-3cf1-4a28-8fca-13fef7a20418",536879060]],["^15",[2980,"^K",1754249596250,536879060]],["^15",[2980,"^@",false,536879060]],["^15",[2980,"^Y","middle-earth",536879060]],["^15",[2980,"^11","Middle-earth",536879060]],["^15",[2980,"^B",1754249596250,536879060]],["^15",[2980,"^;","~u688fb97c-eee6-456f-8701-4ccac060776c",536879060]],["^15",[2987,"^K",1754249959152,536879127]],["^15",[2987,"^@",false,536879127]],["^15",[2987,"^Y","middle-earth/languages/shibboleth",536879127]],["^15",[2987,"^A",2979,536879127]],["^15",[2987,"^11","Middle-earth/languages/shibboleth",536879127]],["^15",[2987,"^B",1754249959152,536879127]],["^15",[2987,"^;","~u688fbae7-2aef-427e-b8e2-f2aacfca647f",536879127]],["^15",[2988,"^12",2,536879138]],["^15",[2990,"^12",2,536879145]],["^15",[3016,"^12",2,536879678]],["^15",[3020,"^Q","It is tempting to think that analogy-making must be a subtle and deep intellectual process that always serves a grand cognitive goal and is always utilized in a serious and eﬃcient manner. Yet all sorts of analogies that we humans come up with lead nowhere at all and lend no support to any prior mental project we might have had on any scale whatsoever. Quite to the contrary: since analogies emerge as an automatic by-product of our cognitive mechanisms, which are at all times searching for familiar-looking landmarks in unfamiliar landscapes before us, they frequently have no\nls-type:: annotation\nhl-page:: 518\nhl-color:: yellow\nid:: 68924991-383c-4727-9945-525d41207af2",536879714]],["^15",[3020,"^O","^1;",536879714]],["^15",[3020,"^@",false,536879714]],["^15",[3020,"^F",2972,536879714]],["^15",[3020,"^X",2302,536879714]],["^15",[3020,"^V",2302,536879714]],["^15",[3020,"^U",2302,536879715]],["^15",[3020,"^?",["^ ","^1Y","annotation","^1Z",518,"^1[","yellow","^1D","68924991-383c-4727-9945-525d41207af2"],536879714]],["^15",[3020,"^J",["^14",["^1Y","^1Z","^1[","^1D"]],536879714]],["^15",[3020,"^4",["^ ","^1Y","annotation","^1Z","518","^1[","yellow","^1D","68924991-383c-4727-9945-525d41207af2"],536879714]],["^15",[3020,"^;","~u68924991-383c-4727-9945-525d41207af2",536879714]],["^15",[3021,"^Q","depth or insight. In a word, many of the analogies we make are utterly pointless and lead nowhere at all.\nls-type:: annotation\nhl-page:: 519\nhl-color:: yellow\nid:: 689249b0-4392-4470-ad65-6a890661b47a",536879728]],["^15",[3021,"^O","^1;",536879728]],["^15",[3021,"^@",false,536879728]],["^15",[3021,"^F",3020,536879728]],["^15",[3021,"^X",2302,536879728]],["^15",[3021,"^V",2302,536879728]],["^15",[3021,"^U",2302,536879729]],["^15",[3021,"^?",["^ ","^1Y","annotation","^1Z",519,"^1[","yellow","^1D","689249b0-4392-4470-ad65-6a890661b47a"],536879728]],["^15",[3021,"^J",["^14",["^1Y","^1Z","^1[","^1D"]],536879728]],["^15",[3021,"^4",["^ ","^1Y","annotation","^1Z","519","^1[","yellow","^1D","689249b0-4392-4470-ad65-6a890661b47a"],536879728]],["^15",[3021,"^;","~u689249b0-4392-4470-ad65-6a890661b47a",536879728]],["^15",[3022,"^Q","the search for samenesses linking situations is so profoundly inherent to thought that trivial, meaningless analogies are tirelessly produced by our subconscious minds, for no reason at all, out of the blue. Analogies pop up and momentarily seize our attention wherever the mind roams.\nls-type:: annotation\nhl-page:: 519\nhl-color:: yellow\nid:: 689249ca-43af-47ca-a8cb-91acebda18e6",536879742]],["^15",[3022,"^O","^1;",536879742]],["^15",[3022,"^@",false,536879742]],["^15",[3022,"^F",3021,536879742]],["^15",[3022,"^X",2302,536879742]],["^15",[3022,"^V",2302,536879742]],["^15",[3022,"^U",2302,536879743]],["^15",[3022,"^?",["^ ","^1Y","annotation","^1Z",519,"^1[","yellow","^1D","689249ca-43af-47ca-a8cb-91acebda18e6"],536879742]],["^15",[3022,"^J",["^14",["^1Y","^1Z","^1[","^1D"]],536879742]],["^15",[3022,"^4",["^ ","^1Y","annotation","^1Z","519","^1[","yellow","^1D","689249ca-43af-47ca-a8cb-91acebda18e6"],536879742]],["^15",[3022,"^;","~u689249ca-43af-47ca-a8cb-91acebda18e6",536879742]],["^15",[3023,"^Q","((689249ca-43af-47ca-a8cb-91acebda18e6))",536879755]],["^15",[3023,"^O","^1;",536879751]],["^15",[3023,"^F",2973,536879751]],["^15",[3023,"^X",1000,536879751]],["^15",[3023,"^V",3025,536879767]],["^15",[3023,"^U",1000,536879802]],["^15",[3023,"^U",3022,536879802]],["^15",[3023,"^?",["^ "],536879755]],["^15",[3023,"^H",3022,536879755]],["^15",[3023,"^;","~u689249d4-504c-4efc-9cf6-8aa3a6793802",536879751]],["^15",[3024,"^Q","",536879759]],["^15",[3024,"^O","^1;",536879759]],["^15",[3024,"^F",3988,536885506]],["^15",[3024,"^X",1000,536879759]],["^15",[3024,"^V",3983,536885460]],["^15",[3024,"^U",1000,536885461]],["^15",[3024,"^?",["^ "],536879759]],["^15",[3024,"^;","~u689249d8-7a01-4e19-ba5c-4125f8528696",536879759]],["^15",[3025,"^Q","Analogies often serve no purpose",536879801]],["^15",[3025,"^O","^1;",536879763]],["^15",[3025,"^F",2930,536879767]],["^15",[3025,"^X",1000,536879763]],["^15",[3025,"^V",1411,536879767]],["^15",[3025,"^U",1000,536879764]],["^15",[3025,"^?",["^ "],536879801]],["^15",[3025,"^;","~u68924a0f-1497-42e1-b5e7-c1390b001904",536879763]],["^15",[3026,"^12",2,536879806]],["^15",[3029,"^Q","Knight